Installation Instructions:

Building and installing requires the tools 'meson' and 'ninja'

Your distribution likely has these tools available, but if not you can
aquire or learn more about them at http://mesonbuild.com/ and
https://ninja-build.org/

Steps:

# mkdir build        # Meson will create all built objects in this directory.
# cd build
# meson ..           # Sets up the build and verifies dependencies are met.
# meson configure    # Optional, you can adjust some options here if you want.
# ninja              # Compiles mal-gtk
# ./src/mal-gtk      # Runs mal-gtk
# sudo ninja install # Optional, installs program. Typically to /usr/local/bin
